- Ah, sim?!

633
00:47:39,373 --> 00:47:40,702
Aqui tens.

634
00:48:00,019 --> 00:48:01,263
O que estás a fazer?

635
00:48:02,187 --> 00:48:04,310
A tua carruagem aguarda-te.

636
00:48:05,899 --> 00:48:06,930
A sério?

637
00:48:07,401 --> 00:48:08,682
Eu, no balde?

638
00:48:09,069 --> 00:48:10,728
Sim, confia em mim.

639
